headline: Builders FirstSource (BLDR): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q3 Earnings?
summary: Builders FirstSource has been treading water for the past six months, recording a small loss of 3.6% while holding steady at $124.18. The stock also fell short of the S&P 500’s 8.6% gain during that period.
